---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import SectionBlock from "../components/SectionBlock.astro";
---

<Layout title="About" current="about" description="A local ReFi node and cooperative-in-formation in Barcelona.">
  <SectionBlock title="About ReFi BCN" intro="A local ReFi node and cooperative-in-formation anchored at Bloc4 (Barcelona)." tissue={true} tissueSeed={3}>
    <p>We work at the meeting point of Catalonia's Economia Social i Solidària (cooperatives, community land trusts, time banks) and the regenerative-finance tooling emerging globally — translating between them, surfacing what's useful, refusing the rest.</p>
    <h3>Theory of change</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>ESS ↔ Web3 Bridge</strong> — Translate Web3/ReFi tools into cooperative language and context; bring local ESS projects to global funding channels; co-design governance that respects cooperative values while leveraging decentralized infrastructure.</li>
      <li><strong>Regenerant Catalunya as proof</strong> — €27K+ pooled, 10+ local projects funded, multi-sig treasury operated by local stakeholders. A working model other bioregions can adapt.</li>
      <li><strong>Cooperative formation pathway</strong> — Evolving from informal coordination into a formal cooperative structure (target Q3 2026).</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Team</h3>
    <p>Andrea (positioning + canvas + reference docs) · Giulio (front-end + technical infrastructure) · Luiz (operations + organization)</p>
    <p>Plus partner organizations: Miceli (catalunya.place), La Fundició, Keras Buti.</p>
  </SectionBlock>
</Layout>
